Tools:

Git version control, MS SQL Server, MS Sequel Server Integration Services (SSIS), MS Sequel Server Data Tools, MS Excel Pivot Table


Objective / Scenario:

ETL solution to load from source OLTP to the Product dimension of the Star Schema ROLAP for a recreational vehicle (RRV) manufacturing company scenario. The Product database is the source for the ETL and stores data about Dealers (dealerships that sell the manufactured recreational vehicles), the MMC entity (Make, Model and Class/ information of a vehicle type), Color (color of the manufactured vehicles), Customer (purchaser of at least one RRV), Feature (vehicle feature type and value), Feature Set (set of feature types and values), Incentive program (incentive program the vehicle was sold under), RRV Instance ( physical vehicle manufactured), Sold (physical vehicle sold), Unallocated (unsold or unallocated status), Vehicle Type (vehicle type that describes a unique combination of vehicle make, model class, color and feature sets), Warehouse (unallocated RRV branch storage), and Allocated (dealership allocated RV).



The Product dimension is made up of dimensional attributes given as:

MMC_Make_Name : Name of a make

MMC_Make_Desc : Description of a make

MMC_Model_Name : Name of a model

MMC_Model_Desc : Description of a model

MMC_Class_Name : Name of the class

MMC_Class_Desc : Description of the class

CLR_ID : ID of color

CLR_Description : Description of a color

VT_Model_Year : Model year for an RRV type

VT_ID : ID for a vehicle type

VT_MSRP : Manufacturer's suggested retail proce for the vehicle type

VT_Wholesale_Price : Wholesale price for the vehicle type

MMC_ID : ID for a combination of Make, Model, and Class


 Star schema physical data model
 


Products physical data model






Candidate source mapping for product dimension

 


PROTOTYPING


Staging and ETL plan for product dimension

  );

DDL for view from Product database: Extract Color view
/*
** Run this in SEIS732_Team_10_Products database
**
*/
IF ( EXISTS(SELECT NAME
            FROM   sysobjects
            WHERE  NAME = 'Extract_Color'
                   AND type = 'V') )
  BEGIN
      DROP VIEW extract_color;
  END;

go

CREATE VIEW extract_color
AS
  SELECT DISTINCT clr_id                             AS PRD_Color_ID,
                  '<No Color Name for '
                  + Cast (clr_id AS VARCHAR) + ' >'  AS PRD_Color_Name,
                  '<No Color Description for '
                  + Cast ( clr_id AS VARCHAR) + ' >' AS PRD_Color_Description
  FROM   rrv_instance
  WHERE  clr_id NOT IN (SELECT clr_id
                        FROM   color)
  UNION
  SELECT clr_id          AS PRD_Color_ID,
         clr_name        AS PRD_Color_Name,
         clr_description AS PRD_Color_Description
  FROM   color;

DDL for view from Product database: Extract MMC view

/*
** Run this in SEIS732_Team_10_Products database
**
*/
IF ( EXISTS(SELECT NAME
            FROM   sysobjects
            WHERE  NAME = 'Extract_MMC'
                   AND type = 'V') )
  BEGIN
      DROP VIEW extract_mmc;
  END;

go

CREATE VIEW extract_mmc
AS
  SELECT MC.mmc_id                AS PRD_MMC_ID,
         CL.prd_class_name        AS PRD_Class_Name,
         CL.prd_class_description AS PRD_Class_Description,
         CL.prd_class_key         AS PRD_Class_Key,
         MK.prd_make_name         AS PRD_Make_Name,
         MK.prd_make_description  AS PRD_Make_Description,
         MK.prd_make_key          AS PRD_Make_Key,
         MD.prd_model_name        AS PRD_Model_Name,
         MD.prd_model_description AS PRD_Model_Description,
         MD.prd_model_key         AS PRD_Model_Key
  FROM   mmc MC,
         stage_mmc_class CL,
         stage_mmc_make MK,
         stage_mmc_model MD
  WHERE  MC.mmc_id = CL.prd_mmc_id
         AND MC.mmc_id = MK.prd_mmc_id
         AND MC.mmc_id = MD.prd_mmc_id;

go

DDL for view for Product dimension: Extract Product view

/*
** Run this in SEIS732_Team_10_Products database
**
*/
IF ( EXISTS(SELECT NAME
            FROM   sysobjects
            WHERE  NAME = 'Extract_Product'
                   AND type = 'V') )
  BEGIN
      DROP VIEW extract_product;
  END;

go

CREATE VIEW extract_product
AS
  SELECT RRV.prd_key,
         SVT.prd_vehicletype_id,
         SVT.prd_model_year,
         SVT.prd_manufacturer_suggested_retail_price,
         SVT.prd_wholesale_price,
         MMC.prd_mmc_id,
         CL.prd_color_id,
         CL.prd_color_name,
         CL.prd_color_description,
         CL.prd_color_key,
         MMC.prd_class_name,
         MMC.prd_class_description,
         MMC.prd_class_key,
         MMC.prd_make_name,
         MMC.prd_make_description,
         MMC.prd_make_key,
         MMC.prd_model_key,
         MMC.prd_model_description,
         MMC.prd_model_name
  FROM   stage_rrv_instance RRV,
         stage_vehicle_type SVT,
         stage_color CL,
         stage_mmc MMC
  WHERE  CL.prd_color_id = RRV.prd_color_id
         AND MMC.prd_mmc_id = SVT.prd_mmc_id
         AND SVT.prd_vehicletype_id = RRV.prd_vehicletype_id;

go
